      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. This unit pairs the legendary power plant with a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a torque-sensing M Limited-Slip Differential. Recent preventive maintenance includes a shim-and-bucket valve adjustment and a structural subframe reinforcement. The suspension geometry remains precise, utilizing MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup for exceptional lateral grip. A purist\u2019s example with linear power delivery and an 8,000 RPM ceiling, optimized for the discerning driver.",
